  "description": "CPU and memory pressure, power and connection state, and datastore headroom for ESXi hosts scraped by the pryorda vmware_exporter. Answers \"which host or datastore is about to run out of room, and is anything disconnected?\" rather than dumping raw vCenter counters.",
